	R1. The system must perform process.	
	R1.1. The admin must perform generic task (Perform task one - Perform task 2).	
	R1.1.1. The admin must perform task one.	
	R1.1.2. The admin must perform task 2.	
	R1.1.2.1. If the message "stop message" is received while performing task 2, this task must be cancelled and the admin must perform interrupting task.	
	R1.1.2.2. If the error "system exception" happens while performing task 2, this task must be cancelled and the admin must notify exception. As a result, the signal "error occurred" must be sent.	
	R1.1.2.3. After 1 hour while performing task 2, the admin must perform undoing task.	
	

